casebody.data:
APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2011-0337. AT&T Communications of Ohio v. Lynch.

Cuyahoga App. No. 94320, 2011-Ohio-302. Discretionary appeal accepted. Discretionary cross-appeal not accepted.

Pfeifer, J., would also accept the cross-appeal. McGee Brown, J., would also accept the cross-appeal on Proposition of Law No. I. Lundberg Stratton, O’Donnell, and Cupp, JJ., dissent and would not accept the appeal.
